{"hablante":"A","texto":"What is the date today?"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"Today is Monday, the third of June."},
{"hablante":"A","texto":"See you on the weekend, then!"},
{"hablante":"B","texto":"Yes, see you on Saturday!"}
